The paper discusses a novel unsupervised preprocessor for autonomous learning agents and robots that can handle high-dimensional input streams such as video. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and robotics (cs.RO).
